                   <h1>Explore the Options, Discover Your Talents</h1>
                    
                    <p>As one of the largest and most prestigious banks in the world, Bank of America Merrill Lynch offers a wealth of opportunities to high-calibre people at different levels:</p>
                     <div id="programs">
						 <ul class="nav-programs">
						 <li id="nav-analyst"><a href="#analyst">Analyst</a></li>
						 <li id="nav-associate"><a href="#associate">Associate &amp; Ph.D.</a></li>
						 <li id="nav-internships"><a href="#internships">Internships &amp; Pre-Internships</a></li>
						 </ul>
                     
                         <div id="analyst" class="programs-content">
                         
                         <h2>Graduate Opportunities</h2>
                         
                         <p>Our analyst-level programmes are designed for students completing an undergraduate or master’s degree.</p>

                          <p>When you join us as a university graduate, you’ll learn from the best and brightest minds in the industry. You’ll participate in a comprehensive training programme that combines instructor-led and web-based classes with on-the-job training and networking. We’ll trust you with important work, giving you the opportunity to create real impact right from the start.</p>
                       
                         <p class="learnmore-button"><a href="campus-EMEA-analyst-programs.aspx" title="Learn more about our analyst programmes">Learn more <span class="hiddencontent">about our analyst programmes</span></a></p>

    
                         </div><!--.programs-content-->
                         
                          <div id="associate" class="programs-content ui-tabs-hide">
                         
                        <h2>Associate opportunities</h2>

                        <h3 class="pad-top">MBA Programmes</h3>
                        <p>Leverage the power of your MBA or advanced degree into real career momentum with instructor-led and web-based education, on-the-job training and networking. This is where you combine your education and experience with our incredible range of opportunities—and the sky’s the limit.</p> 
                         <!--<p class="learnmore-button"><a href="campus-EMEA-associate-and-phd-programs.aspx" title="Learn more about our associate and Ph.D. programmes">Learn more <span class="hiddencontent">about our associate and Ph.D. programmes</span></a></p>-->

                        
                        <h3>Quantitative Analytics Programme (Ph.D.)</h3>
                        <p>Pursuing a doctoral degree with a quantitative focus?<br />Our Quantitative Analytics or Global Rates and Currencies Algorithmic Trading programmes are for you. Our Ph.D. programmes enable doctoral students with high-level technical skills to put their intellect and ambition to work in a fast-paced, exciting environment that will challenge and reward a rigorous approach.</p> 
                        
                        <p class="learnmore-button"><a href="campus-EMEA-associate-and-phd-programs.aspx" title="Learn more about our associate and Ph.D. programmes">Learn more <span class="hiddencontent">about our associate and Ph.D. programmes</span></a></p>


                         </div><!--.programs-content-->
                         
                          <div id="internships" class="programs-content ui-tabs-hide">
                         
                         <h2>Internships</h2>
						
						<p>Internships at Bank of America Merrill Lynch are offered at Analyst and Associate levels.</p>

                        <p>An internship is an excellent opportunity to gain insight into working life at the bank and discover which direction you would like to take your career. You’ll work alongside our full-time employees performing real tasks with the potential for measurable impact on our business.</p> 
						
						<p class="learnmore-button"><a href="campus-EMEA-internships.aspx" title="Learn more about our internships">Learn more <span class="hiddencontent">about our internships</span></a></p>

                        <h2>Pre-Internships</h2>
						
						<p>Opportunities are available during the early stages of your degree to take part in day or week-long events to gain an insight into the bank. Prior to joining university, there are also opportunities to learn about the financial services industry and career options available to you before starting to decide your future career path.</p> 
						
						<p class="learnmore-button"><a href="campus-EMEA-pre-university.aspx" title="Learn more about our pre-university opportunities">Learn more <span class="hiddencontent">about our pre-university opportunities</span></a></p>

				
